\p
\v 5 My masterВҰ335035 YahwehВҰ335035 saysВҰ335034, вҖңThat \add brick model\add* is YerushalemВҰ335038 where I've placed her in the middleВҰ335039 of the nationsВҰ335040, andВҰ335042 where I've surrounded her with other \add вүҲcountriesВҰ335040\add*.
\v 6 \add вүҲButВҰ335045 due to her wickednessВҰ335049,\add* she's rejected my decrees more than \add other\add* nationsВҰ335052 have, and \add вүЎavoided\add* my regulations more than the countriesВҰ335058 thatВҰ335059 surround her. HerВҰ335060 people have rejected my judgements and haven't \add вүҲfollowed\add* my regulations.вҖқ
\v 7 Therefore my masterВҰ335076 YahwehВҰ335076 says this, вҖңBecause you're more troublesome than the nations thatВҰ335083 surround you, and haven't \add вүҲfollowed\add* my statutes or obeyed my regulationsВҰ335085, or even acted accordingВҰ335093 to the surrounding nations' regulations,вҖқ
\v 8 therefore my masterВҰ335104 YahwehВҰ335104 saysВҰ335103 this, вҖңListen, I myself will work againstВҰ335107 you. I'llВҰ335111 executeВҰ335111 judgementsВҰ335113 among you for the \add other\add* nationsВҰ335115 to seeВҰ335106.
\v 9 Because of yourВҰ335135 detestable actions, I'll do things to youВҰ335118 thatВҰ335120 I'veВҰ335123 never done before, andВҰ335124 which I'll never do againВҰ335131:
\v 10 FathersВҰ335149 will eat children among you, and sons will eat theirВҰ335145 fathersВҰ335145, since I'llВҰ335146 executeВҰ335146 judgementВҰ335148 onВҰ335142 you and scatterВҰ335149 all of you who are left inВҰ335142 every direction.вҖқ\x + \xo 5:10: \xt Lam 4:10.\x*
