\v 11 This is my masterВҰ335165 Yahweh's declaration: As \add surely as\add* I live, it's certainly becauseВҰ335170 you've defiled my sanctuaryВҰ335173 with all your hateful things, and with all \add вүҲthe disgusting things you've done\add*, that I myself will reduce you in numberвҖ”\add вүҲI\add* won't have pity on you, and I won't spare you.
\v 12 A third of you will die by plagueВҰ335196, plusВҰ335198 they'll be consumed by a famineВҰ335198 \add вүҲthat comes to you\add*. A third will die by \add вүҲviolence\add* \add in the area\add* surrounding you. Then I'llВҰ335209 scatter a third in every direction, and draw out a sword to chase afterВҰ335212 them as well.
