\v 13 ThenВҰ335214 my \add вүҲrage will be over\add*, and I'll \add вүҲend\add* my fury atВҰ335218 them. I'll be satisfied, and they'll knowВҰ335220 that I, YahwehВҰ335224, have spokenВҰ335225 inВҰ335218 my rage \add вүҲand\add* I'veВҰ335225 completed my furious \add punishment\add* of them.
