\v 15 SoВҰ335242 Yerushalem will become something for other people to condemn and to mockвҖ”a warningВҰ335245 and a horrorВҰ335246 to the nationsВҰ335247 that surround you. I'll executeВҰ335250 judgementsВҰ335252 against you inВҰ335250 rageВҰ335256 and fury, and withВҰ335250 an angry rebukeВҰ335255. I, YahwehВҰ335258 have declared that.
