\v 17 I'll sendВҰ335285 a famineВҰ335287 and disasters against you so you'll be childlessВҰ335290. Plague and bloodshedВҰ335292 will passВҰ335293 through you, and I'll bringВҰ335297 a swordВҰ335296 against you. I, YahwehВҰ335300, have declared that.\x + \xo 5:17: \xt Rev 6:8.\x*
\c 6
