\v 6 Everywhere you \add people\add* liveВҰ335374, citiesВҰ335375 will be \add вүҲturned to rubble\add* and the \add вүҲhilltop shrines\add* ruinedВҰ335381, so that your altars will be \add вүҲbroken down and left idle\add*. Then they'll be broken and disappear, your pillars will be cut down, and \add вүҲeverything you people have built\add* will be wipedВҰ335388 away.
\v 7 The dead will fall down \add вүҲright there amongВҰ335393 you\add*, andВҰ335394 you'll knowВҰ335394 that I am YahwehВҰ335398.
