\v 8 вҖң вҖҳ\add вүҲButВҰ335400\add* I'llВҰ335400 preserve a remnant among you, andВҰ335400 there'll be some who escapeВҰ335403 the swordВҰ335404 among the nationsВҰ335405, when you'reВҰ335406 scatteredВҰ335406 throughout the countriesВҰ335407.
\v 9 Then those who escapeВҰ335410 will think about me amongВҰ335412 the nationsВҰ335412 whereВҰ335413 they'll be held captiveВҰ335414. \add вүЎThey'll rememberВҰ335409\add* that I was grieved by their promiscuous heartВҰ335421 that turnedВҰ335425 away from me, andВҰ335409 by their eyesВҰ335428 that \add вүҲlustedВҰ335429\add* afterВҰ335430 their idolsВҰ335431. Then the loathingВҰ335432 for the wickednessВҰ335436 that they've committed withВҰ335412 all their \add вүҲdisgusting activities\add* will show onВҰ335412 their facesВҰ335433,
\v 10 andВҰ335442 they'll knowВҰ335442 that I am YahwehВҰ335446. It was for a reason that I said I'd bring this evil onto them.вҖҷвҖқ
\s1 Yahweh's punishment of the Israelis
\p
\v 11 My masterВҰ335461 YahwehВҰ335461 saysВҰ335460 this: вҖңClap your handsВҰ335464 and stampВҰ335465 your feet. Say, вҖҳOh dear,вҖҷ because of all the \add вүҲdisgustingly evil things done by the IsraeliВҰ335475 people\add*, because \add now\add* they'll fall by swordВҰ335478, famineВҰ335479, and plagueВҰ335480.
\v 12 \add вүҲThose who are far from\add* \add Yerushalem\add* will die by plagueВҰ335484, and those who are near will fall by the swordВҰ335487. Those who remainВҰ335489 and survive will die by famineВҰ335491. \add вүҲThat's the way that\add* I'llВҰ335493 put my fury against them \add вүҲinto action\add*.
\v 13 ThenВҰ335497 you'll know that IВҰ335500 am YahwehВҰ335501, when their dead lie among their idols, aroundВҰ335506 their altarsВҰ335507, on every high hillвҖ”on all the mountainВҰ335516 peaks, and under every flourishing tree and thick oakвҖ”the placesВҰ335527 whereВҰ335528 they burned incense to all their idols.
\v 14 I'llВҰ335537 strike the land withВҰ335550 my handВҰ335540 and make \add вүҲit bare and deserted\add* from the wildernessВҰ335548 to DiblahВҰ335549, throughout all the placesВҰ335551 where they liveВҰ335551. ThenВҰ335537 they'll knowВҰ335552 that I am YahwehВҰ335556.вҖқ
\c 7
