\v 8 вҖңNow before long I'llВҰ335659 pour out my fury against you and expend my rageВҰ335660 upon you when I judgeВҰ335665 you accordingВҰ335666 to \add вүҲwhat you do\add* and bring all your \add вүҲdisgusting actions\add* \add back\add* on you,
