\v 10 Look here, the dayВҰ335693вҖ”\add вүҲyes\add*, it's comingВҰ335695. Doom has gone out. The wooden stick has blossomedВҰ335698. Arrogance has buddedВҰ335700.
\v 11 Violence has grown up into a wooden stick of wickednessВҰ335708, \add butВҰ335712\add* none of them \add вүҲ(even though there's many of them)\add*, and none of their wealthВҰ335715, and none of their importance will continue.
\p
\v 12 вҖңThe timeВҰ335722 is comingвҖ”the dayВҰ335724 has comeВҰ335721 close. Don't let a buyerВҰ335725 be happy or a sellerВҰ335729 be sad, because my angerВҰ335734 is \add вүҲdirected at the entireВҰ335737 large group\add*.
\v 13 \add вүҲNo,\add* the sellerВҰ335742 won't returnВҰ335747 to the land he sold as long as they both live, because the visionВҰ335753 concerningВҰ335754 the entireВҰ335756 group won't be reversed, and because of theirВҰ335758 \add вүҲdisobedience\add*, none of them will be \add вүҲable to save themselvesВҰ335765\add*.
