\v 11 When they moved, they went in any of theirВҰ336790 fourВҰ336789 directions, without turning as they went, because whatever direction the headВҰ336800 faced, they went in thatВҰ336797 direction without turning as they went.
\v 12 TheirВҰ336817 whole bodyВҰ336809 (includingВҰ336810 their backsВҰ336810, their handsВҰ336811, and their wingsВҰ336812) was covered with eyes, and there were eyes all aroundВҰ336816 the four wheels, covering them as well.\x + \xo 10:12: \xt Rev 4:8.\x*
