\v 16 Whenever the winged creatures moved, the wheels would go beside them, andВҰ336855 whenever the winged creatures liftedВҰ336860 up theirВҰ336864 wingsВҰ336864 to take off from the earthВҰ336867, the wheels didn'tВҰ336868 turnвҖ”they still stayed beside them.
