\v 1 ThenВҰ336974 the spiritВҰ336976 liftedВҰ336974 me up and broughtВҰ336977 me to the easternВҰ336985 gate of Yahweh's \add вүҲtemple\add*, facing east, and wow, inВҰ336989 the doorway of the gate there were twenty-five men. Among them I sawВҰ336994 Azzur'sВҰ337001 son YaazanyahВҰ336998 and Benayah'sВҰ337007 son Felatyah, \add who were\add* leadersВҰ337008 of the peopleВҰ337009.
