\v 2 \add @Yahweh\add* told me, вҖңHumanity'sВҰ337014 child, theseВҰ337017 are the menВҰ337018 who \add вүҲplan to do evilВҰ337024 things\add* and who make wickedВҰ337020 plans inВҰ337025 this cityВҰ337025.
