\v 7 Therefore the masterВҰ337079 YahwehВҰ337079 saysВҰ337078: The people you've killed, whose bodies you've laid inВҰ337084 the middle of Yerushalem, are the meat, and this city is the pot. ButВҰ337087 you \add people\add* are going to be brought out from the centre of this city.
\v 8 You've fearedВҰ337094 the sword, so I'm bringingВҰ337096 the sword againstВҰ337097 you. That's my masterВҰ337099 Yahweh's declaration.
\v 9 I'll bring you out from the city, andВҰ337102 put you into the handsВҰ337107 of foreigners, because I'll bring judgementВҰ337112 against you \add people\add*.
\v 10 You'll \add вүҲbe killed\add* by the swordВҰ337114. I'llВҰ337120 judgeВҰ337120 you within Yisrael's borders so that you \add people\add* will knowВҰ337122 that I am YahwehВҰ337126.
\v 11 This city won'tВҰ337129 be your cooking pot, nor will you be the meat inside it. I'llВҰ337142 judgeВҰ337142 you \add people\add* within Yisrael's bordersВҰ337140.
\v 12 ThenВҰ337145 you'll knowВҰ337145 that I am YahwehВҰ337149, the one whose instructions you haven't \add вүҲobeyed\add* andВҰ337145 whose regulationsВҰ337151 you haven't \add вүҲfollowed\add*. Instead, you people have \add imitated\add* the \add wicked\add* \add вүҲcustoms\add* of the nationsВҰ337158 that surround you.вҖқ
\p
\v 13 ThenВҰ337163 as I was prophesyingВҰ337164, Benayah'sВҰ337168 son Felatyah diedВҰ337169. \add вүҲSoВҰ337163\add* I fell \add вүҲto my knees with my faceВҰ337173 bowed low to the ground\add* andВҰ337163 criedВҰ337174 out with a loud voiceВҰ337175, вҖңOh no, my masterВҰ337180 YahwehВҰ337180, will youВҰ337183 completelyВҰ337182 \add вүҲeliminate the IsraeliВҰ337186 people\add*?вҖқ
