\p
\v 14 Then YahwehВҰ337193 \add вүҲgave me this\add* messageВҰ337191:
\v 15 вҖңYour brothers, humanity'sВҰ337199 child, your brothers and all the \add вүҲIsraeliВҰ337206 peopleВҰ337202 who were exiledВҰ337203\add*вҖ”the ones living in YerushalemВҰ337213 say about them all, вҖҳThey're far away from YahwehВҰ337216. \em This land\em* was givenВҰ337219 to us as \add вүҲours to ownВҰ337221\add*.вҖҷ
