\v 16 So tell \add them\add*, вҖҳMy masterВҰ337229 YahwehВҰ337229 saysВҰ337228 this: вҖҳAlthough I've removedВҰ337232 them far away \add вүҲto other\add* nationsВҰ337233, and though I've scatteredВҰ337235 them among \add &those\add* lands, I myself have been a \add вүҲplace of security\add* for them for a littleВҰ337240 while inВҰ337233 the lands whereВҰ337242 theyВҰ337244 \add вүҲwere taken\add*.вҖҷ
