\v 17 So \add explain\add* \add to them\add*, вҖҳMy masterВҰ337253 YahwehВҰ337253 saysВҰ337252 this: вҖҳI'll gatherВҰ337255 you from the peopleВҰ337259 groups, and assembleВҰ337260 you from the landsВҰ337264 where you were scatteredВҰ337266, and I'll giveВҰ337268 you \add back\add* the \add вүҲcountryВҰ337264\add* of YisraelВҰ337273.вҖҷ
