\v 20 so that they'll \add вүҲfollow my instructions and obey my regulationsВҰ337309\add*. ThenВҰ337321 they'll be my peopleВҰ337320, and I'llВҰ337322 be their godВҰ337324.
\v 21 \add вүҲButВҰ337326\add* to those who \add вүҲwould rather happily choose\add* their detestableВҰ337329 andВҰ337326 disgusting ways, I'llВҰ337335 \add вүҲmake their actions bounce back\add* onto their own headsВҰ337334. That's the masterВҰ337337 Yahweh's declaration.вҖқ
\s1 God's glory leaves Yerushalem
