\p
\v 22 ThenВҰ337340 the winged creatures liftedВҰ337340 up theirВҰ337344 wingsВҰ337344 and the wheelsВҰ337345 that were besideВҰ337346 them, and the \add вүҲbrilliant light\add* of Yisrael'sВҰ337350 godВҰ337348 was up high over them.\x + \xo 11:22-23: \xt Eze 43:2-5.\x*
