\v 6 As for you, humanity's child, groan \add вүҲas if your pelvis has cracked\add*. Groan \add вүҲbitterly in front of them\add*.
\v 7 \add вүҲThat'll get the people\add* asking you, вҖҳWhat are you groaning about?вҖҷ Then you'll tell \add >them\add*, вҖҳBecause of the news that's coming, because every \add вүҲstomach will go tense\add* and every hand will tremble. \add вүҲBreathing will become difficult\add*, and every knee will \add вүҲturn to jelly\add*. Listen, it's coming, and \add вүҲthat's what it'll be like\add*. That's the master Yahweh's declaration.вҖҷ вҖқ
