\v 26 ItsВҰ343146 priests do violenceВҰ343147 to my law, and they profane my sacred things. They don't distinguishВҰ343156 between sacred and profane things, and don't teach the difference between \add вүҲwhat God approved and what he didn'tВҰ343155\add*. They \add вүҲignore\add* my rest days so I \add end up\add* getting mocked amongВҰ343167 them.\x + \xo 22:26: \xt Lev 10:10.\x*
