\v 28 \add вүҲbutВҰ343183\add* itsВҰ343183 prophetsВҰ343183 have painted them over with whitewashВҰ343186. They see false visions andВҰ343183 predict falsehoods to them, sayingВҰ343192 вҖҳThe masterВҰ343195 Yahweh saysВҰ343194 thisвҖҷ when Yahweh hasn't spokenВҰ343199.
