\v 17 The Babylonians cameВҰ343460 to her and to her bed of lust, and they defiled her withВҰ343469 theirВҰ343469 promiscuity. \add Yes,\add* she'd defiled herself by what she'd done, \add вүҲso\add* she turnedВҰ343473 herself away from them inВҰ343469 disgust.
