\p
\v 1 Then YahwehВҰ345126 \add вүҲgave\add* me \add another\add* messageВҰ345124:
\v 2 вҖңNow you, humanity'sВҰ345133 child, begin a \add вүҲfuneral song\add* about Tsor \add (TyreВҰ345137)\add*,
\v 3 andВҰ345140 tell Tsor (\add вүҲwhichВҰ345142 is on a coastal island\add*вҖ”merchants to peopleВҰ345149 groups on many \add other\add* islands) thatВҰ345142 the masterВҰ345156 YahwehВҰ345156 saysВҰ345155 this to you:
\q1 Tsor, you'veВҰ345160 saidВҰ345160, вҖҳ\add вүҲMy beautyВҰ345163 has reached perfectionВҰ345162\add*.вҖҷ
\q1
\v 4 Your bordersВҰ345167 are \add вүҲsurrounded by the ocean\add*.
\q1 Your buildersВҰ345168 have perfectedВҰ345169 your beautyВҰ345170.\f + \fr 27:4 \ft Here, the island city of Tyre is imagined as a ship in the ocean.\f*
