\v 9 \add вүҲExperienced craftsmen\add* from Geval \add вүҲsealed\add* your seamsВҰ345237.
\q1 All the shipsВҰ345240 and theirВҰ345242 sailorsВҰ345242 among you were carrying your merchandiseВҰ345246 for tradeВҰ345245.
\q1
\v 10 \add вүҲWarriors from\add* Persia, Lydia, and Libya were inВҰ345252 your army.
\q1 They hung their shieldsВҰ345255 and helmetsВҰ345256 within youВҰ345259.
\q1 They displayed your splendourВҰ345262.
