\p
\v 20 Then YahwehВҰ345898 \add вүҲgave\add* me \add another\add* messageВҰ345896:\x + \xo 28:20-26: \xt Yoel 3:4-8; 1Ki 11:4-5; 1Ki 16:30-33.\x*
\q1
\v 21 вҖңHumanity's child, \add вүҲlook towards\add* Tsidon \add (SidonВҰ345909)\add* andВҰ345910 prophesyВҰ345910 againstВҰ345907 itВҰ345911.
\v 22 Tell \add them\add* that the masterВҰ345916 Yahweh saysВҰ345915 this: вҖҳListen, I'm againstВҰ345919 you, Tsidon, because I \add вүҲintend to\add* be \add вүҲpraised by you\add*, so yourВҰ345922 peopleВҰ345923 will knowВҰ345923 that I am Yahweh, when I executeВҰ345928 justice within you andВҰ345913 demonstrate my holinessВҰ345931 to you.
\v 23 I'llВҰ345934 sendВҰ345934 a plague to \add afflict\add* you, and \add there'll be\add* bloodВҰ345938 inВҰ345936 your streetsВҰ345939, and \add вүҲpeople will fall dead all around you\add*. WhenВҰ345934 the swordВҰ345943 comes against you from all around, thenВҰ345934 you'll knowВҰ345946 that I am YahwehВҰ345950.
\s1 The blessing for Yisrael
\rem /s1 Israel Will Be Blessed
\q1
\v 24 ThenВҰ345952 there'll no longer be prickingВҰ345959 briars andВҰ345952 painful thornsВҰ345960 for the \add вүҲIsraeliВҰ345956 people\add* from all those aroundВҰ345963 her who despiseВҰ345964 her, so thenВҰ345952 they'll knowВҰ345966 thatВҰ345959 I am the masterВҰ345969 YahwehВҰ345969.вҖҷ
\rem /s1 Future Blessing for Israel; Restoration for Israel
\p
\v 25 The masterВҰ345976 YahwehВҰ345976 says that when I gatherВҰ345978 the \add вүҲJewish peopleВҰ345986\add* from the \add вүҲnations\add* that they were scatteredВҰ345988 among, and when they \add вүҲproperly honour\add* me so the nations may see, then they'll make theirВҰ345997 homes inВҰ345978 the land I gave to my servantВҰ346000 Yakov \add (Jacob)\add*.
\v 26 ThenВҰ346003 they'll live securely within \add @the land\add* and buildВҰ346006 housesВҰ346007, plantВҰ346008 vineyardsВҰ346009, and live securely. WhenВҰ346003 I executeВҰ346012 justice onВҰ346012 all the people all aroundВҰ346017 who now despiseВҰ346015 them, thenВҰ346003 they'll knowВҰ346018 that I am theirВҰ346022 godВҰ346022 YahwehВҰ346021.вҖҷвҖқ
